{"tid":1366603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真心一問 點解我地唔去禮崩府搵林鄭媽媽","createTime":"2019-07-26T04:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T04:59:19.000Z","uid":72301,"like":10,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"de3e01ca665e1f2804f3eb2d75adfdc0d63832a3","tid":1366603,"uid":72301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:05:11.000Z","msg":"佢既然咁唔想見我地<br />\n我地就去請佢面對群眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信好多和理非 中立 以至好似肥媽果種藍都會同意我地政治問題政治解決<br />\n希望可以係暑假完之前嘅搵個星期日 <br />\n召集200萬人直接圍禮賓 對準林媽媽<br />\n表達我地嘅意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話 希望大家玩pokeman go 可以平平安安 <br />\n一個訓練家都不能少！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374609d1ba1beac974d92487a2591fc7ea13e6bf","tid":1366603,"uid":72301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:06:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ab10d2958f5d3f4c2ac3c4b698a2d283e22766","tid":1366603,"uid":72301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:08:06.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e6976e26169706c3cc48996d0451177bb1a948","tid":1366603,"uid":268692,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:10:52.000Z","msg":"你一入紙花園道入口就設防啦 冇入紙好多人唔敢去<br />\n迎賓館附近環境差 難撤退"},{"pid":"7aa47eb04b29b37f76940ffc9152853bb718bbd3","tid":1366603,"uid":72301,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:14:23.000Z","msg":"推啊<br />\n支線要打  但唔好唔記得主線係咩！<br />\n林鄭媽媽就係猜皇帝入面嘅皇帝<br />\n前面本來已經有黑警做守衛<br />\n依家仲要多左班鄉黑幫佢擋多層<br />\n我係林鄭都偷笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gi